Constraints.name: Constraints
Constraints.description: The custom object to hold the various constraints along with their thredholds, source and traget objects
Constraints.label: Constraints

fields.name: SourceField
fields.label: Source Field
fields.description: Source Object Field on which constraint is evaluated

fields.name: Active
fields.label: Active
fields.description: Default: false, Enabale or disables the constraint

fields.name: Max
fields.label: Max
fields.description: Maximum value applicable for the constraint

fields.name: Unit
fields.label: Unit
fields.description: Unit for the Min/Max values. e.g hours, days, minutes

fields.name: Period
fields.label: Period
fields.description: Period over which the constraint is evaluated - Daily, Weekly, Monthly

fields.name: Source
fields.label: Source
fields.description: Source Object on which constraint is evaluated

fields.name: Target
fields.label: Target
fields.description: Target Object on which constraint is evaluated

fields.name: TargetField
fields.label: Target Field
fields.description: Target Object Field on which constraint is evaluated

fields.name: Operator
fields.label: Operator
fields.description: Operator to be applied between Source and target values e.g. -, sum, avg, +, <, >

fields.name: Name
fields.label: Name
fields.description: Name of the Constraint e.g. Overnight Break Scheduled

fields.name: Type
fields.label: Type
fields.description: Type of constraint e.g. Overnight Break, Weekly Days

fields.name: Min
fields.label: Min
fields.description: Minimum value applicable for the constraint
